long_description    ${description}

homepage            http://rocksdb.org/

checksums           rmd160  fd7533a6f5ad3f7c45bca6930738cc505bfb6d0d \
                    sha256  f4a4a8c3d7a961403027310dfa2ffba9519b3a96a0ba0bd0482562757ad5bfdd

